{"tid":921410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄烏危機 德國總理：不會用軍事方式解決","createTime":"2018-11-29T14:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T14:31:25.000Z","uid":60545,"like":6,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa2622e877adceda63fe789fa83d74cd8326fab","tid":921410,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:06:24.000Z","msg":"（法新社柏林29日電） 德國總理默克爾（Angela Merkel）今天表示，烏克蘭危機「沒有軍事解決方案」。烏克蘭總統波洛申科（Petro Poroshenko）曾要求北大西洋公約組織（NATO）海軍支持烏克蘭。<br />\n<br />\n默克爾指責俄羅斯引發緊張情勢，她說：「我們要求烏克蘭方面要明智，因為我們知道，唯有透過講道理和對話才能解決問題，也因為這些爭端沒有軍事解決方案。」（譯者：葉俐緯/核稿：林治平）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/俄烏危機-德國總理梅克爾-沒有軍事解決方案-130502003.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E4%BF%84%E7%83%8F%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%90%86%E6%A2%85%E5%85%8B%E7%88%BE-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88-130502003.html&d=2fkDh5FmsjrViBEEKUDa%2Fxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=aed60606\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/俄烏危機-德國總理梅克爾-沒有軍事解決方案-130502003.html</a>"},{"pid":"08e1aa345dd97854a85c18073b80b7c80d6d9f68","tid":921410,"uid":121146,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:08:41.000Z","msg":"德國婆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母死賤種  食屎啦去"},{"pid":"22f30fdb59fec75c353afa4f9c53270082f9fe0e","tid":921410,"uid":60749,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:10:51.000Z","msg":"大愛左膠真係戇鳩鳩 <br />\n如果德國唔係左膠當道<br />\n可以發展成咩地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0704a3816b3de460b9bf19f6d787b4cd8337df","tid":921410,"uid":38904,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:11:1